research, and advising clients on their import and export activities.

Assignment International Market Development Plan
1. Based on their professional qualities we selected a team out of a pool of consultants and researchers to start our own marketing research and consultancy company. Of course this top company also has its own special name and logo.

2. We had to find a client – a company that wants to expand internationally and wants our consultancy team to research one particular international market thoroughly and present our findings and recommendations.

Company profile: the company should was middle size or a large company that was planning to expand internationally; the company should be selling consumer products/services and applying B2C business model. The company chosen by our group was Izi-Fes B.V. from Rotterdam, Nederlands. 

The research process had two phases:

(a) During the first phase of the project we were asked to solve a particular management problem and give specific recommendations and solutions to the problem. In order to do that, we undertook research into a country and presented our findings in a Marketing Research Report. The country we researched was Germany. This part of the project will take place in term 7.

(b) During the second phase of the project we consulted the client on how to export their product/service to this particular country and what is the best strategy to apply. In order to do that we wrote a complete export plan. This part of the project will take place in term 8.
